3000 REM  LoadSprites — read pixel data and assign to objects 1-4
3010 REM ============================================================
3020 SUB LoadSprites STATIC
3025 SHARED G1S$, G2S$, G3S$, BS$
3030 PS$="16,16," : READ NPS
3040 FOR I=1 TO NPS : READ C$ : PS$=PS$+C$ : NEXT I
3050 G1S$="16,16," : READ NG1S
3060 FOR I=1 TO NG1S : READ C$ : G1S$=G1S$+C$ : NEXT I
3070 G2S$="16,16," : READ NG2S
3080 FOR I=1 TO NG2S : READ C$ : G2S$=G2S$+C$ : NEXT I
3090 G3S$="16,16," : READ NG3S
3100 FOR I=1 TO NG3S : READ C$ : G3S$=G3S$+C$ : NEXT I
3105 BS$="16,16," : READ NBS
3106 FOR I=1 TO NBS : READ C$ : BS$=BS$+C$ : NEXT I
3110 OBJECT.SHAPE 1, PS$
3120 OBJECT.SHAPE 2, G1S$
3130 OBJECT.SHAPE 3, G2S$
3140 OBJECT.SHAPE 4, G3S$
3150 OBJECT.SCALE 1, 2
3160 OBJECT.SCALE 2, 2
3170 OBJECT.SCALE 3, 2
3180 OBJECT.SCALE 4, 2
3190 END SUB
